id: pm-tnud
title: "Consolidate package lifecycle: extension/package/install/upgrade under a single pm package namespace"
description: "extension and package (already partial synonyms) plus top-level install and upgrade unify under pm package <verb> (install/upgrade/list/describe/enable/disable/...); extension, install, upgrade become hidden aliases. Duplicate check: pm-jqd2/pm-3wsi/pm-b3e9 are install-behavior bugs/hints, not surface consolidation."
