assignee: codex-agent
author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 240
acceptance_criteria: pm package covers the full extension/install/upgrade verb set with flag parity; extension/install/upgrade spellings alias-shimmed with identical output; scope semantics (project/global) unchanged; contracts/MCP/completions/docs regenerated; existing extension+install+upgrade specs pass via aliases
